<section class="questions">
  <div class="paragraph centered font-sans">
    <p>First, think about the areas that are most dangerous to you by thinking about your triggers. What kind of relapse are you most likely to have (crystal, high­risk sex, or both)?</p>
  </div>

  <div class="textarea centered">
    <textarea class="1"><%= answer_1 %></textarea>
  </div>

