    <p>What high­risk behaviors can you change? Consider such things as getting clean needles, making sure that you have condoms, planning to have different kinds of sex?</p>
  </div>

  <div class="textarea centered">
    <textarea class="2"><%= answer_2 %> </textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="paragraph centered font-sans">
    <p>What support systems and resources (both friendships and activities) can you activate to reduce the amount of time you use and help you get back into recovery?
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="textarea centered">
    <textarea class="3"><%= answer_3 %> </textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="paragraph centered font-sans">
    <p>As you have become more familiar with the relationship between crystal and sexuality, what have you learned about being able to stop thoughts of drug use?
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="textarea centered">
    <textarea class="4"><%= answer_4 %></textarea>
  </div>
  
 <div class="paragraph centered font-sans">
    <p>￼What have you learned about being able to stop high­risk sex fantasies?</p>
  </div>

